revision.text: ==English== ===Proper noun=== {{en-proper noun|Yankeys}} # {{surname|en}}. ===Statistics=== * According to the 2010 United States Census, ''Yankey'' is the 30630<sup>th</sup> most common surname in the United States, belonging to 761 individuals. ''Yankey'' is most common among White (74.77%) and Black/African American (21.68%) individuals.
